Modern Chelsea Living | Contemporary 3-Bed Apartment with Stylish Interiors & Exceptional Connectivity\
\
This beautifully finished 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment with an additional powder room offers refined modern living in one of London's most desirable postcodes. Combining contemporary design, bright open-plan interiors and thoughtful detailing throughout, this impressive 1493 sq ft residence provides an ideal home for professionals seeking style, comfort and superb transport links in the heart of Chelsea district.
